GENERIC BOARD/CARD GAME RECORD TEMPLATE
793.93 — Board & Card Games (Systems, Records, Rules, Play Logs)
========================================================
BOARD_OR_CARD_GAME_RECORD Γ
========================================================

GAME_ID: <unique identifier>
GAME_NAME: <string>
VERSION: <string>

--------------------------------------------------------
PLAYERS
--------------------------------------------------------
P := { p1, p2, ..., pn }

For each player pi:
    pi.ID            : <string>
    pi.Name          : <string>
    pi.Score         : <int or map>
    pi.Hand          : <list of card IDs>        ; card games
    pi.Pieces        : <list of piece IDs>       ; board games
    pi.Resources     : <map>                     ; optional
    pi.Status        : <active | eliminated | etc>

--------------------------------------------------------
COMPONENTS
--------------------------------------------------------
Deck D (if applicable):
    D.ID             : <string>
    D.Cards          : <list of card IDs>
    D.Discard        : <list of card IDs>

Board B (if applicable):
    B.ID             : <string>
    B.Layout         : <ASCII or symbolic>
    B.Zones          : <list>
    B.Pieces         : <map of piece → location>

Tokens / Resources:
    T := { t1, t2, ..., tk }
    Each t:
        t.ID         : <string>
        t.Type       : <currency | victory | etc>
        t.Owner      : <player ID or neutral>

--------------------------------------------------------
TURN_STRUCTURE
--------------------------------------------------------
Turn τ_k:
    τ_k.ID           : <int>
    τ_k.Player       : <player ID>
    τ_k.Phase        : <DRAW | MAIN | ACTION | END>
    τ_k.Timestamp    : <time>

--------------------------------------------------------
ACTION_LOG
--------------------------------------------------------
Action α_k:
    α_k.ID           : <string>
    α_k.Turn         : <turn ID>
    α_k.Player       : <player ID>
    α_k.Action       : <PLAY_CARD | MOVE_PIECE | DRAW | DISCARD | BUY | TRADE>
    α_k.Targets      : <list of card IDs, piece IDs, or zones>
    α_k.Result       : <state change>
    α_k.Timestamp    : <time>

--------------------------------------------------------
RANDOM_LOG
--------------------------------------------------------
Random event r_k:
    r_k.ID           : <string>
    r_k.Source       : <shuffle | draw | dice | spinner>
    r_k.Dist         : <distribution>
    r_k.Outcome      : <value>
    r_k.Timestamp    : <time>

--------------------------------------------------------
STATE_SNAPSHOTS
--------------------------------------------------------
Snapshot s_k:
    s_k.ID           : <string>
    s_k.Turn         : <turn ID>
    s_k.Player_Hands : <map>
    s_k.Board_State  : <map>
    s_k.Resources    : <map>
    s_k.Metadata     : <optional>

--------------------------------------------------------
SCORING
--------------------------------------------------------
Score entry σ_k:
    σ_k.ID           : <string>
    σ_k.Player       : <player ID>
    σ_k.Change       : <int>
    σ_k.Reason       : <objective | card effect | territory>
    σ_k.Timestamp    : <time>

--------------------------------------------------------
TERMINAL_OUTCOME
--------------------------------------------------------
Terminal state s_T:
    s_T.ID           : <string>
    s_T.Turn         : <turn ID>

Outcome ω:
    ω.Winner         : <player ID or tie>
    ω.Final_Scores   : <map>
    ω.Metadata       : <optional>

--------------------------------------------------------
EQUIVALENCE_METADATA (optional)
--------------------------------------------------------
Canonical_Form       : <normalized game tree ID>
Transformations      : <list of applied equivalence ops>
Distance_Vector      : <metrics>

========================================================
